content:
Javelin heads are a members-only item, and are used to make javelins. Smithing a metal bar or cutting an amethyst will yield 5 javelin heads. Each head requires a javelin shaft to make it into a javelin.

  • Iron javelin heads

  • Mithril javelin heads
  • Adamant javelin heads
  • Rune javelin heads

Crafted

  • Amethyst javelin heads

Only dropped

  • Dragon javelin heads
